CMake           >= 3.0.0                        http://www.cmake.org
libqt           >= 5.5.0                        http://www.qtsoftware.com
libkde          >= 5.5.0                        http://www.kde.org
libkipi         >= 5.0.0                        https://projects.kde.org/projects/kde/kdegraphics/libs/libkipi
Hugin           >= 0.8.0 (runtime dependency)   http://hugin.sourceforge.net
Enblend         >= 3.0.0 (runtime dependency)   http://enblend.sourceforge.net

